snippet: U.S. banks posted stronger-than-expected trading results in the second quarter due to surprisingly active markets in June, but bank executives stopped short of saying the good times would continue....

headline.print_headline: For Big U.S. Banks, June's Trading Bonanza May Not Persist: Executives
headline.main: For Big U.S. Banks, June's Trading Bonanza May Not Persist: Executives

lead_paragraph: U.S. banks posted stronger-than-expected trading results in the second quarter due to surprisingly active markets in June, but bank executives stopped short of saying the good times would continue.
